<P><H1 align=center>FIND CUSTOMER – CR010</H1>
<P></P>
<P>This screen is used as a search facility for existing applications.</P>
<P>If you are entering a new applicants details that are not currently held on the 
system, there is no need to enter any details on this screen. Just click the button 
New Customer. Else:- </P>
<P>Input what is known of the Surname, Forename(s), Customer Number, Date of 
Birth and Postcode. If the full details are not known, you can search for all 
possible entries by entering at least the first letter of the surname followed 
by an asterix (‘*’) as a wildcard. You must enter the minimum of an asterix in 
the ‘Forename(s)’ field. A Date of Birth and Postcode (if known) can be used to 
further refine the search.</P>
<P>Click on the Search button and the system will search for the application.All 
matching entries found in the database will be displayed in the Search Results 
box.</P>
<P>Highlight the relevant customer from the list of customers displayed and 
click on the Select button . This will take you to the next 
screen.</P>

